name: Gambá-mãe e o baarara
description: An animation about the opossum mother and a person that sing "baarara" behind the wall. Here where I live have a lot of opossum that sometimes walking in the yard.  I even sung in the bathroom to compose this animation. :)  This opossum is Brazilian specie.  The resolution of the .mp4 is 854x480 (480p).
